<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM2.10.3">
<l>koḻuntalaru malarccōlaik kuḻāṅkoḷ poykaik kōḷmutalai vāḷeyiṟṟuk koṇṭaṟ keḷki</l>
<l>yaḻuntiyamā kaḷiṟṟiṉukkaṉ ṟāḻi yēnti yantaramē varattōṉṟi yaruḷcey tāṉai</l>
<l>eḻuntamalark karunīla miruntil kāṭṭa virumpuṉṉai muttarumpic cempoṉ kāṭṭa</l>
<l>ceḻuntaṭanīrk kamalantī vikaipōl kāṭṭun tirukkōva lūrataṉuḷ kaṇṭēṉ nāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The one who granted mercy appearing when he came mid-air,</l>
<l rend="indent">bearing a discus that day for [the sake of] the great elephant,</l>
<l>Which was clasped fearing being taken in the sharp teeth</l>
<l rend="indent">of a vicious crocodile [in] a pond set in a cluster of gardens</l>
<l rend="indent">with buds that open [into] blooms,</l>
<l>I saw in Tirukkōvalūr where lotuses appear like lamps</l>
<l rend="indent">in the beautiful pond waters,</l>
<l>As dark blue lotuses with blossoms risen [high] appear [like] coal,</l>
<l rend="indent">and as pearl [buds] of excellent laurels bursting appear [like] fine gold.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
